{"tid":219618,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有警員放工搵女報案人做朋友","createTime":"2017-04-27T10:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T14:41:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b265b442cd917058f9347fcdb39ae687cbd503a8","tid":219618,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20003177&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20003177%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170427&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=b9fe252c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20003177%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170427&h=5cff1276\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20003177&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170427</a><br />\n<br />\n有警員放工搵女報案人做朋友<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】監警會副秘書長（行動）梅達明（圖右）昨在會上表示，近年平均每年接獲5至6宗涉及休班警員的投訴。他指，曾接獲投訴指有警員在執行職務時，取得女性報案人的聯絡資料，並於休班後聯絡對方。他批評，有關做法是不恰當及不專業，並提醒警員要避免同類型情況發生，「可能你搵嗰個人佢願意同你做朋友，唔嚟投訴，我亦都有見過隔咗幾年，我同你分手後先嚟投訴都有，你永遠唔會贏嘅情況，你好彩嘅佢唔嚟投訴，但呢個行為我哋覺得係唔恰當」。<br />\n<br />\n休班警拘疑犯　監警指應表揚<br />\n<br />\n另一涉及休班警務人員的投訴個案顯示，一名休班警長目睹有人在港鐵車廂內突然襲擊一名女乘客，隨即與另外兩名乘客上前制服對方，在掙扎期間，該警長披露警員身份，及後亦拘捕對方。<br />\n事發後，該名警長被對方指控濫用職權及揑造證據。監警會認為警長行為屬執行職務，故同意投訴警察課調查結果，將兩項指控列為「並無過錯」。另外，監警會亦建議警方對警長見義勇為的表現加以讚賞。<br />\n■記者紀靜雯"},{"pid":"b9f3213f23dc31fe8db1835ddc560b0d6ffdf30c","tid":219618,"uid":37834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:44:41.000Z","msg":"善用政府資源，叻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6919add1090563c0aa90e2fb9da18c7e8a124fe3","tid":219618,"uid":107279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果係靚仔既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca8bedb652f182d2592eadda1146bcbb361ce72","tid":219618,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:38:29.000Z","msg":"阿sir無即場強姦你算賺左啦"},{"pid":"6bd47ca7b8de42d5935e0d51c8b36288df78b698","tid":219618,"uid":13151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿sir無即場強姦你算賺左啦</blockquote><br />\n啊sir強姦唔使你教"}]}